					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2046631#post-2717337</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2046631/empedocles#post-2717337</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 29 Dec 2016 23:51:01 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>WrongJohnSilver</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2000367</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gaffney" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1324229&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1483055887" alt="Gaffney" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1324229)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gaffney" >Gaffney</a></span> had asked for something related to the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/fifthist-hub">Fifth Church</a>, connected to a historical event. I ended up going way back.</p> <p>For your edification:</p> <p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Empedocles" target="_blank">Empedocles</a> invented the concept of the classical elements.<br /> <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hippocrates" target="_blank">Hippocrates</a> came up with the concept of four humors and embraced natural causes for disease.<br /> <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Socrates" target="_blank">Socrates</a> was just this guy, you know.<br /> <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Euripides" target="_blank">Euripides</a> was a famous playwright; <em>Medea</em> is the oldest play in the Western canon we still perform today.<br /> <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anaxagoras" target="_blank">Anaxagoras</a> finished up just as Socrates was getting started.<br /> <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pausanias_of_Sicily" target="_blank">Pausanias</a> was Empedocles' student and <em>eromenos</em>, which is best translated today as &quot;lover.&quot;</p> <p>&#8230;And yes, this is related to On Mount Golgotha as well.</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2303803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1483055887" alt="Cyantreuse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2303803)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" >Cyantreuse</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1414765&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1483055887" alt="Doctor Cimmerian" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1414765)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" >Doctor Cimmerian</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1483055887" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" >Roget</a></span> for their thoughts and advice at various stages of this thing.</p> 
				 	]]>
